The K8S location modifier will:
  - replace all org.alien4cloud.extended.container.types.ContainerRuntime by org.alien4cloud.extended.container.types.kubernetes.abstract.Container
    - fill it's properties
  - replace all org.alien4cloud.extended.container.types.ContainerDeploymentUnit by org.alien4cloud.extended.container.kubernetes.resource.Deployment
  - wrap all orphean org.alien4cloud.extended.container.types.ContainerRuntime into a org.alien4cloud.extended.container.kubernetes.resource.Deployment
  - for each container capability of type endpoint, add a org.alien4cloud.extended.container.kubernetes.resource.Service and weave depends_on relationships
  - analyse relationships between containers : when a relationship exist between 2 container, if not exist a relationship of type depends_on should be added between surrounding Deployment objects
    - if a relationship already exist between 2 Deployments but in the other way, throw an exception
